metadata.name: BattleVerse Pass #1
metadata.description: DAR BattleVerse Membership NFT is a early access card that allows you to download BattleVerse beta. With exclusive in-game features that include weapons, skin packs, health, special abilities as well as 1 RARE NFT when BattleVerse goes LIVE. Every month members will receive a weapon NFT that they may use in the game or sell it to someone looking for that specific weapon. Once the NFT is minted, the member can follow the DARtoken.io website and go to the BattleVerse link that only NFT members will have access to. They will also be able to claim their NFTâ€™s and download special content.
